<ol>
    <li>Research and select appropriate AI frameworks and libraries.</li>
    <li>Integrate AI components into the existing architecture.</li>
    <li>Test AI functionalities in a controlled environment.</li>
    <li>Implement automatic Ollama server startup on demand.</li>
    <li>Deploy AI features in production and monitor performance.</li>
</ol>

<h2>Future Enhancements</h2>
<p>Explore additional AI capabilities such as predictive analytics, automated content generation, and advanced server lifecycle management.</p>
